capping
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:The NZ university graduation ceremonies (held usu. in May), and the attendant activities, the University ceremony (and the various student activities associated with it) of formal presentation of a degree ? ca1900; capping day, capping week, capping magazine.
